data.description: Beautiful 2 bedroom, 2 bath home. Hardwoods in the entry area that leads to the Spacious vaulted family room, Dining Room combo with fireplace. Bright kitchen all appliances. Sunroom off of kitchen. Master bedroom features trey ceiling, walk-in closet, and bath with walk in shower. Secondary bedroom and full bath down the hall. The laundry room is conveniently located near master bedroom. Two car garage. Come be a part of this Wonderful 55+ community with pool, tennis, clubhouse, and social events that is close to shopping. Lawn maintenance included in HOA dues.
